title: Excalibur's Outdoor America
overview: Excalibur's Outdoor America, produced by Wolf Creek Productions, is one of the longest running series on Outdoor Channel. Since its debut in 1994, EOA has delivered quality outdoor entertainment for the whole family, focusing primarily on big game hunting in North America. Beginning in 2017, EOA will be hosted by veteran outdoor TV personality Joe Thomas. Joe will be joined by other celebrity guests like Fred Eichler and various other familiar faces. Made by real hunters, for real hunters. Don't miss one heart pounding minute of Excalibur's Outdoor America!
